gitalen Zwilling\ngebaut?","position":{"start":{"line":73,"column":1},"end":{"line":73,"column":1}},"key":"lNc8IBYfTu"}],"key":"zUlD0z8Kn9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":78,"column":1},"end":{"line":81,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ja und nein. Wir haben ein geometrisch korrektes digitales Modell des Objekts\nerzeugt (Meshroom + CloudCompare), und wir haben das Verhalten dieses Objekts\nunter bestimmten Bedingungen simuliert (Python). Das sind die\nKernbestandteile eines digitalen Zwillings.","position":{"start":{"line":78,"column":1},"end":{"line":78,"column":1}},"key":"aOGD5hczVr"}],"key":"XfkPyxjbDG"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":86,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was fehlt, ist die ","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":83,"column":1}},"key":"xLA0OLhWbL"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":83,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"bidirektionale Verknüpfung","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":83,"column":1}},"key":"StED7wm6W9"}],"key":"TdEnO5XW4D"},{"type":"text","value":": Ein vollständiger digitaler\nZwilling würde in Echtzeit Sensordaten vom physischen Objekt empfangen und\nseinen Zustand automatisch aktualisieren. Das ist in industriellen Anwendungen\nStandard, war aber nicht Teil dieser Vorlesung.","position":{"start":{"line":83,"column":1},"end":{"line":83,"column":1}},"key":"IqvhmHdNHE"}],"key":"YGqaYP6Mw9"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"emphasis","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Was hätten wir brauchen, um den nächsten Schritt zu gehen?","position":{"start":{"line":88,"column":1},"end":{"line":88,"column":1}},"key":"CIt6mc7zFZ"}],"key":"dsC4DlwZk0"}],"key":"J03Ur1wt13"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"star